{"tid":412563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖] 集思廣益，如何繼續撚狗","createTime":"2017-09-24T18:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T13:29:06.000Z","uid":145826,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cabcdf035cf0ecb14b7f5409c955b22dfb9e99c4","tid":412563,"uid":145826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹係ig釣左條話自己唔係狗公既狗公<br />\n咁早幾日已經釣左佢出黎{約砲}等左個幾兩個鐘(影曬相)，跟住佢嬲到仆街，我死狗哄返佢，佢而家又問我出唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，點樣可以徹底玩尻條仆街，唔好問我拎圖住，一間紅左就無得揭穿條仆街含家產既真面目<br />\n<br />\nPs 隻狗岩岩溝左個新女唔夠一個月，但又同我講出黎見下識下岩既可以發展，仆街到唔識形容"},{"pid":"223f683076d835b8153c71baa8a15d9ddac5880c","tid":412563,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"夜啦 瞓啦"},{"pid":"301875eca70d34de64639afb37f88447934b18b2","tid":412563,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"圖都無張仲點講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fedd1be48d61aa1dfab894fdcc2bd5b8cd2aea","tid":412563,"uid":145826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖都無張仲點講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見佢又問我出唔了諗住玩多佢一獲，本身諗住close file"},{"pid":"fc55cf59da1845344e7de662eabc72587d8adde2","tid":412563,"uid":92921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a77e8824758045b664f8d28993667176ac22794","tid":412563,"uid":145826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖都無張仲點講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲少少會出返個post，好多圖，包你lam lam 脷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91c24e80f865fa4f8cfd10211001e61db71321c","tid":412563,"uid"